## рҹ“Ұ Enums

### SeatCategory
```python
class SeatCategory(Enum):
    VIP = "VIP"            # вӮ№5000 - Front rows
    PREMIUM = "PREMIUM"    # вӮ№2000 - Middle sections
    REGULAR = "REGULAR"    # вӮ№500  - Back sections
```

### SeatStatus (Critical for Locking!)
```python
class SeatStatus(Enum):
    AVAILABLE = "AVAILABLE"  # Can be selected
    LOCKED = "LOCKED"        # Temporarily held (10 min)
    BOOKED = "BOOKED"        # Confirmed booking
```

### BookingStatus
```python
class BookingStatus(Enum):
    PENDING = "PENDING"      # Seats locked, awaiting payment
    CONFIRMED = "CONFIRMED"  # Payment done, booking complete
    CANCELLED = "CANCELLED"  # User cancelled
```

