| locked_until | DateTime | Lock expiry |
| booked_by | User | Who booked it |
| price | int | Price for this concert |

### Simplified Approach (For Interview):
Just use a dict in Concert:
```python
self.seat_status = {seat_id: SeatStatus.AVAILABLE for seat in venue.seats}
self.seat_locks = {}  # seat_id -> {user, expires_at}
```

