## рҹ“қ Design Decisions Summary

| Decision | Choice | Reasoning |
|----------|--------|-----------|
| Seat status | Per-concert | Same seat can be available for different concerts |
| Locking | 10 minute hold | Industry standard, prevents abandonment issues |
| Max seats | 10 per booking | Prevent scalping |
| Refund | >24h only | Common policy |
| Concurrency | Lock-first wins | Simple, effective |
| Singleton | ConcertBookingSystem | Central management |

