## вҡ пёҸ Common Interview Mistakes

| Mistake | Why It's Wrong | Correct Approach |
|---------|----------------|------------------|
| Forget Seat entity | Can't track individual seat status | Add Seat class |
| Seat status on Venue | Same seat status for all concerts | Seat status per Concert |
| No locking mechanism | Race conditions | Add LOCKED status + timer |
| No max seat limit | Scalping possible | Limit to 10 per booking |
| Forget lock expiry | Seats stuck forever | Background check or lazy check |

